title: Enjoying Physical Intimacy as a Woman, Part 6
itunes:author: Guests: Dr. Cliff & Joyce Penner
itunes:summary: A healthy marriage is built on the foundation of open communication. The same is true for your sex life. John and Greg give some ideas for how to talk about sex with your spouse, even when it feels awkward. Receive the book Enjoy! with your gift of any amount!
